# VLX-Seek 3B — Ollama Modelfile (seanlab007 适配版)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VLX-Seek 是 om-ai-lab 发布的细粒度视觉定位 VLM (CVPR 2026)
# 范式: Region Reference (区域引用 token) 而非坐标生成
# 原仓: https://github.com/om-ai-lab/VLX-Seek
# Fork: https://github.com/seanlab007/VLX-Seek
# 协议: Apache 2.0
#
# 用途: 在 ollama 中以 OpenAI 兼容 API 调用 vlx-seek-3b
#       asi-genesis / maoai 通过 http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions
#       即可像调用 llama3 / qwen2.5 一样调用 VLX-Seek
#
# 部署步骤 (权重发布后执行):
#   1. 等待 https://huggingface.co/omlab 发布 vlx-seek-3b gguf
#   2. 下载到 ~/models/vlx-seek-3b/
#   3. cd ~/models/vlx-seek-3b/
#   4. ollama create vlx-seek-3b -f /Users/daiyan/Desktop/VLX-Seek/ollama/Modelfile
#   5. ollama run vlx-seek-3b "describe the image"
#
# 当前状态: 模型权重未发布 (2026-06-28), 此 Modelfile 处于 ready-to-load 状态

FROM /Users/daiyan/models/vlx-seek-3b/vlx-seek-3b-q4_k_m.gguf

# ── 元数据 ──
PARAMETER temperature 0.2
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096
PARAMETER num_predict 1024
PARAMETER stop "<|im_end|>"
PARAMETER stop "<|endoftext|>"

# ── 视觉定位专用 system prompt ──
#   范式: 输出 <ground>区域描述</ground><object><obj_n></object> token
#   asi-genesis/maoai 客户端解析这个 token 流, 映射回 bbox 坐标
SYSTEM """You are VLX-Seek, a fine-grained perception vision-language model.
When given an image and a referring expression, identify target regions using
the region-reference token format:

  <ground>description of the target region</ground><object><obj_id></object>

Rules:
1. NEVER output raw coordinate numbers. Use region-reference tokens only.
2. When multiple regions match, list them in reading order (top-left first).
3. If asked to count, output the integer count plus the region tokens.
4. For OCR tasks, embed the recognized text in the ground tag.
5. Be concise. No preamble, no explanation, only structured output."""